OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen it will be mainly dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods overnight, but the odd shower
OL,9,Fpossible in the southwest later.
OL,10,FCloudier at times around the North Sea
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,14,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Becoming
OL,15,Fvery warm, locally hot. Turning
OL,16,Fcloudier in the southwest through the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
