OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fcloudy on Friday with a few showers at
OL,7,Ffirst. Cloudy on Saturday with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain spreading east. Then
OL,9,Fmostly dry on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
